[01:29.02]As Buck slid along with the obscureness of a gliding shadow, his nose was jerked suddenly to the side as though a positive force had gripped and pulled it.  He followed the new scent into a thicket and found Nig.  He was lying on his side, dead where he had dragged himself, an arrow protruding, head and feathers, from either side of his body. 
